19bool CachedTemplateMatches(Isolate* isolate,
20 Tagged<NativeContext> native_context,
21 Tagged<JSArray> entry, int function_literal_id,
22 int slot_id, DisallowGarbageCollection& no_gc) {
23 if (native_context->is_js_array_template_literal_object_map(
24 entry->map(isolate))) {
25 Tagged<TemplateLiteralObject> template_object =
26 TemplateLiteralObject::cast(entry);
27 return template_object->function_literal_id() == function_literal_id &&
28 template_object->slot_id() == slot_id;
29 }
30
31 Handle<JSArray> entry_handle(entry, isolate);
32 Tagged<Smi> cached_function_literal_id =
33 Smi::cast(*JSReceiver::GetDataProperty(
34 isolate, entry_handle,
35 isolate->factory()->template_literal_function_literal_id_symbol()));
36 if (cached_function_literal_id.value() != function_literal_id) return false;
37
38 Tagged<Smi> cached_slot_id = Smi::cast(*JSReceiver::GetDataProperty(
39 isolate, entry_handle,
40 isolate->factory()->template_literal_slot_id_symbol()));
41 if (cached_slot_id.value() != slot_id) return false;
42
43 return true;
44}
45} // namespace

47// static
48Handle<JSArray> TemplateObjectDescription::GetTemplateObject(
49 Isolate* isolate, Handle<NativeContext> native_context,
50 Handle<TemplateObjectDescription> description,
51 Handle<SharedFunctionInfo> shared_info, int slot_id) {
52 int function_literal_id = shared_info->function_literal_id();
53
54 // Check the template weakmap to see if the template object already exists.
55 Handle<Script> script(Script::cast(shared_info->script(isolate)), isolate);
56 int32_t hash =
57 EphemeronHashTable::TodoShape::Hash(ReadOnlyRoots(isolate), script);
58 MaybeHandle<ArrayList> maybe_cached_templates;
59
60 if (!IsUndefined(native_context->template_weakmap(), isolate)) {
61 DisallowGarbageCollection no_gc;
62 // The no_gc keeps this safe, and gcmole is confused because
63 // CachedTemplateMatches calls JSReceiver::GetDataProperty.
64 DisableGCMole no_gcmole;
65 ReadOnlyRoots roots(isolate);
66 Tagged<EphemeronHashTable> template_weakmap =
67 EphemeronHashTable::cast(native_context->template_weakmap());
68 Tagged<Object> cached_templates_lookup =
69 template_weakmap->Lookup(isolate, script, hash);
70 if (!IsTheHole(cached_templates_lookup, roots)) {
71 Tagged<ArrayList> cached_templates =
72 ArrayList::cast(cached_templates_lookup);
73 maybe_cached_templates = handle(cached_templates, isolate);
74
75 // Linear search over the cached template array list for a template
76 // object matching the given function_literal_id + slot_id.
77 // TODO(leszeks): Consider keeping this list sorted for faster lookup.
78 for (int i = 0; i < cached_templates->length(); i++) {
79 Tagged<JSArray> template_object =
80 JSArray::cast(cached_templates->get(i));
81 if (CachedTemplateMatches(isolate, *native_context, template_object,
82 function_literal_id, slot_id, no_gc)) {
83 return handle(template_object, isolate);
84 }
85 }
86 }
87 }
88
89 // Create the raw object from the {raw_strings}.
90 Handle<FixedArray> raw_strings(description->raw_strings(), isolate);
91 Handle<FixedArray> cooked_strings(description->cooked_strings(), isolate);
92 Handle<JSArray> template_object =
93 isolate->factory()->NewJSArrayForTemplateLiteralArray(
94 cooked_strings, raw_strings, function_literal_id, slot_id);
95
96 // Insert the template object into the cached template array list.
97 Handle<ArrayList> cached_templates;
98 if (!maybe_cached_templates.ToHandle(&cached_templates)) {
99 cached_templates = isolate->factory()->NewArrayList(1);
100 }
101 cached_templates = ArrayList::Add(isolate, cached_templates, template_object);
102
103 // Compare the cached_templates to the original maybe_cached_templates loaded
104 // from the weakmap -- if it doesn't match, we need to update the weakmap.
105 Handle<ArrayList> old_cached_templates;
106 if (!maybe_cached_templates.ToHandle(&old_cached_templates) ||
107 *old_cached_templates != *cached_templates) {
108 Tagged<HeapObject> maybe_template_weakmap =
109 native_context->template_weakmap();
110 Handle<EphemeronHashTable> template_weakmap;
111 if (IsUndefined(maybe_template_weakmap)) {
112 template_weakmap = EphemeronHashTable::New(isolate, 1);
113 } else {
114 template_weakmap =
115 handle(EphemeronHashTable::cast(maybe_template_weakmap), isolate);
116 }
117 template_weakmap = EphemeronHashTable::Put(isolate, template_weakmap,
118 script, cached_templates, hash);
119 native_context->set_template_weakmap(*template_weakmap);
120 }
121
122 // Check that the list is in the appropriate location on the weakmap, and
123 // that the appropriate entry is in the right location in this list.
124 DCHECK_EQ(EphemeronHashTable::cast(native_context->template_weakmap())
125 ->Lookup(isolate, script, hash),
126 *cached_templates);
127 DCHECK_EQ(cached_templates->get(cached_templates->length() - 1),
128 *template_object);
129
130 return template_object;
131}
